objects.text:
Bring the correct number
of followers to the lava.

If a follower touches another
person they will be converted.
Don't bring too many!

If you stay above your followers
they will follow you from below.

If you made a mistake
press Shift+R or jump in
lava to try again.

Sometimes, you can't get
your hands dirty.
Hold Down or S to Call your minions together.

Hold Z to zoom out.
Press Shift+Z to stay zoomed out.
Don't forget about calling your followers!

Wana-Haya'yuh is not a
spike trap god…
...Nor a fall from height god
Oooh… Pointy!

Spikes are a neat way to
get rid of little mistakes...

Prophets are too proud
to do half-jumps.
These faces look familiar…
BAR
Wana-Friz
Wana-Bern

Old prophets do not make
for strong fighters.
But disposable minions do!
